- to ignore untracked files, add file/directory to .gitignore file at project root directory

- to ignore tracked files, git update-index --assume-unchanged <file>

- git work flow
  - git branch my_branch
  - git checkout my_branch
  - git push origin my_branch
  - git branch --set-upstream my_branch origin/my_branch
  - git add <file>
  - git commit -m "commit message"
  - git pull origin master
  - git push origin my_branch
